                    >
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div
                    class="px-4 pb-3 hidden faq-answer text-sm text-gray-700"
                  >
                    In school and standardized tests, the most common
                    conversions involve length (cm, m, km, in, ft, mi), area
                    (m², ft², acres), volume (mL, L, cups, gallons), mass (g,
                    kg, oz, lb), temperature (°C, °F, K), and time (seconds,
                    minutes, hours, days). This calculator covers all of these
                    and shows the steps for each conversion.
                  </div>
